OL,3,CSearch underway after five people die
OL,4,Cduring cave scuba dive in Maldives
OL,6,FThe search is continuing for the
OL,7,Fbodies of four Italian divers who died
OL,8,Fin a scuba accident in a deep
OL,9,Funderwater cave in the Maldives on
OL,10,FThursday, according to officials.
OL,12,FFive divers, including an instructor,
OL,13,Fwere believed to have been exploring a
OL,14,Fcave in the Vaavu Atoll coral reef
OL,15,Fwhen they went missing, according to
OL,16,FMaldivian presidential spokesperson
OL,17,FMohamed Hussain Shareef.
OL,19,FThe body of the fifth diver has
OL,20,Falready been recovered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
