PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778889776
OL,3,CSearch underway after five people die
OL,4,Cduring cave scuba dive in Maldives
OL,6,FItaly's foreign ministry said the
OL,7,Fcaves are at a depth of 50 metres and
OL,8,Fthat the circumstances of the divers'
OL,9,Fdeath remain under investigation.
OL,11,FThe University of Genoa named the
OL,12,Fvictims as professor of ecology Monica
OL,13,FMontefalcone, her daughter Giorgia
OL,14,FSommacal, who was also a student,
OL,15,Fresearch fellow Muriel Oddenino and
OL,16,Fmarine biology graduate Federico
OL,17,FGualtieri.
OL,19,FThe fifth victim has been named as
OL,20,Fboat operations manager and diving
OL,21,Finstructor Gianluca Benedetti.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778889776
OL,3,CSearch underway after five people die
OL,4,Cduring cave scuba dive in Maldives
OL,6,FIn a statement posted on its website,
OL,7,Fthe university said: "The sympathy of
OL,8,Fthe entire university community goes
OL,9,Fout to the families, colleagues and
OL,10,Fstudents who shared their human and
OL,11,Fprofessional journey."
OL,13,FMaldivian officials say rescuers
OL,14,Frecovered one body from about 60
OL,15,Fmetres below the surface, but that a
OL,16,Ffirst round of searches failed to
OL,17,Flocate the remaining divers, who were
OL,18,Fthought to be inside the same cave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
