PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778889776
OL,3,CSearch underway after five people die
OL,4,Cduring cave scuba dive in Maldives
OL,6,F"The cave is so deep that divers, even
OL,7,Fwith the best equipment, do not try to
OL,8,Fapproach," Shareef said.
OL,10,FThey have described their major search
OL,11,Foperation, which includes boats,
OL,12,Faircraft, and dive teams, as high-risk.
OL,14,FThe search teams are doing a second
OL,15,Fdive on Friday, but rough weather
OL,16,Fconditions could delay the recovery,
OL,17,Fand Maldivian officials may seek
OL,18,Finternational assistance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
