PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778889776
OL,3,CSearch underway after five people die
OL,4,Cduring cave scuba dive in Maldives
OL,6,FItaly's foreign ministry said its
OL,7,Fambassador and an expert were
OL,8,Fassisting the Maldivian coast guard in
OL,9,Fthe search operation.
OL,11,FThe group had been on a morning dive
OL,12,Fnear Alimathaa and was reported
OL,13,Fmissing after failing to surface by
OL,14,Fmidday, according to initial reports.
OL,16,FConditions were described as
OL,17,Funfavourable at the time, with a
OL,18,Fyellow weather alert in effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
